taineruniface_104rjw1665702779670.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rjw1665702779670.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rjw1665702779670.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rjw1665702779670\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                       \n TXT Data Packing\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rjw1665702779670__txt_data_packing_177456\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface maps Uniface packing codes in the fixed part of the record to character string versions of the packing code. It writes fields in the variable part of the record in their conceptual format. However, the TXT connector does not support conversion of binary data, so only String-based packing codes (known as <dfn class=\"term\">Text</dfn> packing codes) should be used in the variable part of a record.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjw1665702779670__p_d61802e1_d61803e1_d61804e1\">Each packing code is mapped to a Text packing code with a length and format that is most suited to the type of the data to be stored.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"rjw1665702779670__table_d5429e1_d5430e1_d5431e1_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"rjw1665702779670__table_d5429e1_d5430e1_d5431e1_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"rjw1665702779670__table_d5429e1_d5430e1_d5431e1\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-filter\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-filter\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Defined Packing Code-0-0\" id=\"topic-Defined Packing Code-